<a id="article1.body1.sec2.p9" name="article1.body1.sec2.p9"></a><p>Of 61 CSF samples from 27 patients on TBM therapy for between 2 days and 9 months, 16 were positive by one of the four methods. Seven samples were positive by MODS. Eight samples were positive by smear, 10 by MGIT and 9 by LJ (<a href="#pone-0001173-t005">table 5</a>).</p>
